quran[9{c,v,t}:
21,36,"yeh munkareen haq jab tumhe dekhte hain to tumhara mazaq bana letay hain kehte hain"" kya yeh hai woh shakhs jo tumahray khudaon ka zikar kya karta hai ?"" aur un ka apna haal yeh hai ke Rehman ke zikar se munkir hain"
21,37,"ensaan jald baz makhlooq hai abhi mein tum ko apni nishanain dukhaay deta hon, jaldi nah macha-o"
21,38,"yeh log kehte hain"" aakhir yeh dhamki poori kab ho gi agar tum sachey ho """
21,39,"kash inn kafiroon ko uss waqt ka kuch ilm hota jabkay yeh nah apne mun aag se bacha saken ge nah apnipithain, aur nah un ko kahin se madad puhanche gi"
21,40,woh bulaa achanak aeye gi aur aِnhin iss terhan yak lakht daboch le gi ke yeh nah is ko dafaa kar saken ge aur nah inn ko lamha bhar mohlat hi mil sakay gi
21,41,"mazaq tum se pehlay bhi Rasolo-n ka uraya ja chuka hai, magar unn ka mazaq urane walay usi cheez ke phair mein aa kar rahay jis ka woh mazaq uratay thay"
21,42,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, inn se kaho,"" kon hai jo raat ko ya din ko tumhe Rehman se bacha sakta ho ?"" magar yeh apne rab ki nasiyaat se mun mourr rahay hain"
21,43,kya yeh kuch aisay khuda rakhtay hain jo hamaray muqablay mein un ki himayat karen? woh nah to khud apni madad kar satke hain aur nah hamari hi taied unn ko haasil hai
21,44,asal baat yeh hai ke inn logon ko aur inn ke aaba o ajdaad ko hum zindagi ka sir o samaan diye chalay gay yahan taq ke inn ko din lag gay magar kya aِnhin nazar nahi aata ke hum zameen ko mukhtalif simtao se ghta-tay chalay aa rahay hain? phir kya yeh ghalib aa jayen ge ?
